            . I am a <rs id="t18300415-246-viclabel1360" type="occupation">broker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-246-victim2144 t18300415-246-viclabel1360"></join>, and live in Wardour-street - the prisoner was my <rs id="t18300415-246-deflabel1361" type="occupation">shopman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-246-defend2142 t18300415-246-deflabel1361"></join>, and was to receive money for me, which he was to bring to me or my wife; he never accounted to me for 10l., received from Mr. Clark, who had purchased a table of me for nine guineas, and I sent it home.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300415-246-person2145">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CLARK
               <interp inst="t18300415-246-person2145" type="surname" value="CLARK"></interp>
